<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Comments.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">This is a new species to the Afrotropical Region and only collected from Uganda. The female remains unknown, despite the fact that 28 males were collected or encountered in various collections.</paragraph>
